{"article_id":"1t6wp3CK1UrCmGWX","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"As thousands of consumers receive health insurance cancellation notices ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"President Obama is continuing to fine tune his promise","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that Americans","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"who like their health plans","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"would be able to keep them under his signature health care law .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"The president told about 200 of his campaign supporters and health care activists Monday","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"that the administration had promised Americans","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"they could keep their current coverage","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"-- as long as their plans hadn ' t changed","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"since ObamaCare was signed into law .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"`` If you have or had one of these plans","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"before the Affordable Care Act came into law","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"and you really liked that plan ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"what we said was you could keep it","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"if it has n't changed","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"since the law 's passed , ''","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"Obama said .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"`` So we wrote into the Affordable Care Act","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"you are grandfathered in on that plan .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"if the insurance company changes it ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"then what we 're saying is they have got to change it to a higher standard .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"They 've got to make it better . ''","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"Obama said","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"his health care law is making the insurance market better for everyone ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"even though millions of Americans","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"who buy individual plans","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"have been receiving cancellation notices .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"the notices `` can be scary for people , ''","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"but added","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"they were often getting `` a very bad deal . '' `` The bottom line is --","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"is that we are making the insurance market better for everybody","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"and that 's right thing","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"to do , ''","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"The president also acknowledged","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"that technical problems with the health care website","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"to shop for insurance","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"are making it tougher for people to find other plans .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"he 's `` not happy about it , ''","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"but promised ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"`` We 're going to smooth this thing out . ''","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"At least 3.5 million Americans have been issued cancellations ,","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"but the exact number is unclear ,","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"The Associated Press reported .","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"In a speech at Boston 's Faneuil Hall this past week , Obama said","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"the problem is limited to fewer than 5 percent of Americans","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"``","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"who 've got cut-rate plans","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"that do n't offer real financial protection in the event of a serious illness or an accident . ''","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"In the Republican-controlled House , officials say","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"a vote is likely as early as next week on a bill","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"to let insurers continue selling any individual policies","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"that were in effect on Jan. 1 , 2013 ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"even if they provide coverage","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"deemed insufficient under Obamacare .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"The measure ,","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"drafted by Rep. Fred Upton , R-Mich. ,","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"and backed by roughly 100 fellow Republicans ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"would remain in effect throughout 2014 ,","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"after which the issue would presumably be reviewed .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"`` Despite the president 's repeated promise","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"of 'if you like your plan ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"you can keep it ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"' many Americans are now learning the sad reality","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"that their current plan will no longer exist","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"beginning on January 1 , ''","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Upton , chairman of the Energy and Commerce Committee , said in a statement","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"when he announced his legislation last week .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"`` This legislation is about providing folks the peace of mind","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"that they will be allowed to keep their current coverage","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"if they so choose . ''","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"While Upton 's legislation permits insurers to sell existing coverage plans","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"that would otherwise be banned ,","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Sen. Mary Landrieu , D-La. , introduced legislation during the day","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"to go one step further","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"by requiring it .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Aides told The Associated Press","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"that under her measure , insurance companies would be obliged to continue offering existing paying customers continued coverage under any plans in effect at the end of 2013 .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"No new consumers could enroll .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"`` A promise was made","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"if you like your health plan ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"you can keep it -","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"and I will do everything","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"I can","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"to see","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"that the promise is kept , ''","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"said Landrieu ,","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"who is gearing up for what is expected to be a challenging re-election campaign next year .","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"Both measures are designed","depth":3},{"id":93,"text":"to cut through a complicated system","depth":4},{"id":94,"text":"in which some plans for individuals","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"that fall short of coverage standards","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"are allowed to continue under Obamacare ,","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"while others are not .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":195,"left":149,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":141,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":102,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":0,"right":101,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":1,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":99,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":119,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":106,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":5,"right":105,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":105,"left":6,"right":104,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":104,"left":7,"right":103,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":112,"right":117,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":112,"left":111,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":108,"right":110,"relation":"co